prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, flat 2D vector illustration in a dreamy fantasy art style. In a whimsical, magical forest, Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are transformed into cheerful cartoon characters. They are seated at a low wooden picnic table, having a hilarious birthday feast. Jordan, on the right in his maroon shirt, is laughing with a wide-open smile while playfully trying to catch a piece of flying sushi in his mouth with chopsticks. Lao Lao, on the left in her dark shirt, has a huge, joyful grin, watching him with amusement. The tabletop is covered with an assortment of comically oversized sushi rolls—a giant California roll, a massive salmon nigiri, and a dragon roll that looks like a miniature, friendly dragon. Two funny cartoon dogs, a Corgi and a Shiba Inu, are sitting on either side of the table, wearing tiny party hats and looking up at the sushi with hopeful, wide eyes. The background is an ethereal, glowing forest with soft-focus, pastel-colored trees, gentle floating light particles, and whimsical, oversized, glowing mushrooms. The overall color palette is magical and soft, with pastel pinks, purples, and blues, creating a warm and enchanting atmosphere. Centered in the middle of the design, beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a soft cream color reads: "Happy Birthday Lao Lao".
